sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Main Thread
    participant BG as Background Task
    participant FS as File System

    UI->>UI: User clicks "Load"
    UI->>UI: Show loading indicator
    UI->>BG: Spawn async task
    BG->>FS: Read file (async)
    UI->>UI: Handle other events
    UI->>UI: Render frames
    FS-->>BG: File contents
    BG->>BG: Parse data
    BG->>UI: Update with results
    UI->>UI: Hide loading indicator
    UI->>UI: Render data
